<h2 id="工程技巧核心公式表" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#工程技巧核心公式表"><span>工程技巧核心公式表</span></a></h2>
<h3 id="_1-target-network" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_1-target-network"><span>1. Target Network</span></a></h3>
<h4 id="purpose" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#purpose"><span>Purpose</span></a></h4>
<ul>
<li>Stabilize bootstrapping</li>
</ul>
<h4 id="formula" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#formula"><span>Formula</span></a></h4>
<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>r</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>γ</mi><munder><mrow><mi>max</mi><mo>⁡</mo></mrow><msup><mi>a</mi><mo mathvariant="normal" lspace="0em" rspace="0em">′</mo></msup></munder><mi>Q</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><msup><mi>s</mi><mo mathvariant="normal" lspace="0em" rspace="0em">′</mo></msup><mo separator="true">,</mo><msup><mi>a</mi><mo mathvariant="normal" lspace="0em" rspace="0em">′</mo></msup><mo separator="true">;</mo><msup><mi>θ</mi><mo>−</mo></msup><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">y = r + \gamma \max_{a&#x27;} Q(s&#x27;, a&#x27;; \theta^-)
