<h3 id="_2-experience-replay" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_2-experience-replay"><span>2. Experience Replay</span></a></h3>
<h4 id="purpose-1" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#purpose-1"><span>Purpose</span></a></h4>
<ul>
<li>Break correlation</li>
<li>Improve sample efficiency</li>
</ul>
<h4 id="update-same-as-q-learning" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#update-same-as-q-learning"><span>Update (same as Q-learning)</span></a></h4>
<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><mi>Q</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>s</mi><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi>a</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>←</mo><mi>Q</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>s</mi><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi>a</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>+</mo><mi>α</mi><mo fence="false" stretchy="true" minsize="1.2em" maxsize="1.2em">(</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>Q</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>s</mi><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi>a</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo fence="false" stretchy="true" minsize="1.2em" maxsize="1.2em">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">Q(s,a) \leftarrow Q(s,a) + \alpha \big(y - Q(s,a)\big)
